<p id="notice"><%= notice %></p>

<h1>Songmap</h1>

<p>Thousands of songs have been written with street names in their title. This map shows you where the streets that influenced the songwriters are located. 
  Explore the music or take a walk down the streets using Goolge Street View </p>


<br>

<p> Is your favorite song about a street missing? <%= link_to 'Please add it!', new_song_path %> </p>

<%= tag.div nil, id: 'map', data: { songs: @songs.to_json(methods: [:address])}  %>


<table>
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>Name</th>
      <th>Artist</th>
      <th>Album</th>
      <th colspan="3"></th>
    </tr>
  </thead>

  <tbody>
    <% @songs.each do |song| %>
      <tr>
        <td><%= song.name %></td>
        <td><%= song.artist %></td>
        <td><%= song.album %></td>
        <td><%= link_to 'Show', song %></td>
        <td><%= link_to 'Edit', edit_song_path(song) %></td>
        <td><%= link_to 'Destroy', song, method: :delete, data: { confirm: 'Are you sure?' } %></td>
      </tr>
    <% end %>
  </tbody>
</table>
